{"tid":1826769,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求，堅持到底，可以嗎？","createTime":"2020-01-16T11:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T12:36:29.000Z","uid":299223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48b760778f99306b75bdba27cf3fa13bdfc7a386","tid":1826769,"uid":299223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T11:36:17.000Z","msg":"如果要完成五大訴求，<br />\n<br />\n其實有<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真&middot;雙普</span></span>選，<br />\n<br />\n其餘都可以輕鬆、真正地達到。<br />\n<br />\n例: 真係可以清算到 <span style=\"color: blue;\">黑警</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">狗官</span> 嘅<span style=\"color: gold;\">獨立調查委員會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可惜嘅係</span><br />\n<br />\n依家嘅風向慢慢咁變左而<span style=\"color: maroon;\">進攻功能組別</span><br />\n<br />\n話要嘗試影響選特首嘅結果<br />\n<br />\n亦即係所謂 <span style=\"color: green;\">plan A plan B</span> 嘅策略。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問問，都半年啦<br />\n<br />\n各位都應該知道五大訴求並唔包括<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">柒婆下台</span>，又或者<span style=\"color: maroon;\">進功能組別</span>嫁何?<br />\n<br />\n所謂<span style=\"color: green;\"> plan a 同 plan b </span>策略係建基於<br />\n<br />\n為左達到同一個目的上，<br />\n<br />\n而當A唔可行嘅時候，就用B去達到同一個目的。<br />\n<br />\n錯誤例子:<br />\n目的: <span style=\"color: blue;\">黑警</span>好可惡，要清算佢地<br />\n<br />\nPlan A: 獨立調查委員會<br />\nPlan B: 自己加入警隊，內部改革<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人權及民主法</span></span>裏面明明講到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港2020雙普選</span>係必須，否則就可能取消獨立關稅地位。<br />\n<br />\n我又真係唔明，點解唔<ins>食住上</ins>?<br />\n<br />\n同<ins>美帝</ins>講我地真真正正須要嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n等佢地放香港入<ins>中美貿易談判第二階段</ins>到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果個制度本身係壞嘅，你重係個制度到同佢玩<br />\n<br />\n咁樣米姐係代表我地重信任個壞左嘅制度?<br />\n<br />\n更何況我地係個制度同佢玩左咁多年都係乜到爭取唔到呢？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n送上一張好有意思嘅FarCry3 quote.<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ffhYSwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FffhYSwx.jpg&h=1b4e95e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後，</span><br />\n<br />\n我人言微輕，只係其中一位抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n可以做嘅就只有發下夢，貼下連儂牆，同做Twitter戰線<br />\n<br />\n我真係好希望具影響力嘅人士，或者政黨，甚至海外遊說團<br />\n<br />\n可以三思而後行<br />\n<br />\n真係可以做到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，堅持到底。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文長，抱歉。"},{"pid":"bbb4437184ffeb699767781e57a4907f45c6c243","tid":1826769,"uid":315780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"支線任務一定要做，但係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 堅持到底</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf32263059bfeb023007ba2a36cd6537876d681","tid":1826769,"uid":311566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"幫唔到樓主推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}